4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a machine learning-based approach for solving a robotics problem, which falls under the broader umbrella of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the problem of mapping robot and scope parameters to workspace, which is a control problem.
